project_descr: Joint Programme on Gender and Women's Empowerment

outputs.output_descr: The initiative aims to support training initiative for women to empower them by promoting sustainable farming and business skills in responsive to gender and climate aspects. Aligned with the EEP, this initiative will be implemented as a pilot before fully rolling out the other initiatives of agricultural supply development and County business center. It will ultimately support building capacity of women smallholder farmers and MSEs in sustainable farming and business development.
